# Starting point for a new brand. Uncomment + set the right-hand suffix
# to your car integration's real entity suffix. Leave a line as
# "<token> <token>" (no-op) if your car uses the same name. Delete lines
# for entities your car does not expose (those cards degrade on their own).
#
# canonical (BYD)          your car's suffix
#front_left_tire_pressure   front_left_tire_pressure
#front_right_tire_pressure  front_right_tire_pressure
#rear_left_tire_pressure    rear_left_tire_pressure
#rear_right_tire_pressure   rear_right_tire_pressure
#location                   location
#power_system               power_system
#state_of_health            state_of_health
#exterior_temperature       exterior_temperature
#odometer                   odometer
#cabin_temperature          cabin_temperature
